Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介回来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打了 别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停 暂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恭介他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 是理树啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我昨晚通宵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介不在时他们俩一直忍着没打架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你在就能随时过去调解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我来定个规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方都空手的话 真人优势太大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的 都拿着竹刀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾优势又太大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们随手扔点武器给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越没用的东西越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩抓到什么就用什么做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为全是没有实用性的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,较之现在这种状态就安全多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗 开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香蕉?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你捧着只猫干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的武器 有意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说用这玩意怎么打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等的铃大人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准欺负弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者? 是说你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是这只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你们打架的理由是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙编了「茅厕顿开」这词来坑我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜其所赐 今天我和人家交谈时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意间说了「真是茅厕顿开啊」用到了这个错词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这理由也太渺小了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你主动跑来问我「茅厕顿开」的意思的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你说的是茅塞顿开这词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就回答了你这词是指突然理解了某一事态而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就交代清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茅厕顿开是啥意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 这下你知道责任在哪边了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用猫爪撕裂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你是恭介的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围观的 扔点武器过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳗…鳗鱼派…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原君 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不仅限于今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是自童年相识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们玩成一片时起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不断重复着的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那最痛苦的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我失去双亲后没多久的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自闭的我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们四个出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强敌出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝 理树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们上 理树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你们是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩治罪恶的正义伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那的确是个强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进行了英勇奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人 我们不会忘记你的牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没拜托你们这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是热闹日子的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样和他们度过一段时光后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知不觉间忘记了心中的痛楚和寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心被快乐充实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终开始祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的时光能永远持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 今天惨透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不叫小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是新来的还没名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫列侬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列侬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你取名字总是这么随便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因斯坦 盖茨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥德丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说恭介 这次你去哪儿应聘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社 东京的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走路去东京!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱啊 我有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们明年也三年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对也会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反正是不会徒步去求职的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 的确如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年后我们不是在准备升学考试就是在求职了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止都在一起的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业后也可能各奔东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能说的是 一年后恭介肯定不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才懒得去想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么遥远的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在这个状态能一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 像过去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体指什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想啊 上小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了找寻罪恶走遍了很多地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我和你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介一直是我们的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他带领我们做出那些激动人心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做只有现在才能做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们组个棒球队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队名就叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那儿 你就站在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 你当投手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说这么分配的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样从发展角度来看会更热血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么的发展?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Little Busters队的比赛必须感人且具有戏剧性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成是受漫画影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树 你去当接球手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 值得纪念的第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开球仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我扔…这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全力扔过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 我直说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予你「神级零控」称号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,434)\fs21}No Control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃得到了「神级零控」称号!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,434)\fs21}No Control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Little Busters目前的活动室就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为棒球社好像出了点纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名义上是废部状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为什么选择棒球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我升上三年级后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直到处求职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其间突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我应该会成为上班族 一直忙于工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这只是因为周边的人都决定了走这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不经意间随波逐流了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了不间断地主张自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定开始打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 听到中途还算明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一句无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为了自我主张而打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球从哪蹦出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁会在求职期间打棒球?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个的确没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般没人会有这个打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟我们一毛钱关系都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为副将 责任也不小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自我主张我选择挥剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去吧 理树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总有一天会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我们都还完全没理解的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1853年佩利 驶入浦贺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你不用做功课的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这不正在做嘛 看就明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来他居然要打棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实让人始料未及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介就是那种会让人跌破眼镜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点地球人都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛 又来拉我们打棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 今天有份作业很棘手 帮我一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让收集伟人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟人的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是名言咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫也会从棍子上摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※原句为猴子也会从树上摔下来 顾名思义是指专业人士也会有失误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是名言是谚语吧 而且错得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新名言诞生于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.84,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,猫也会从棍子上摔下来 井之原真人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥我也要被叫来男生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没空帮人做作业来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此 我就真心讲几句名言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们看看我「那孩子还有点帅喔」的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这句我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:30.78,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真白痴! 枣铃(仰视着旧友·井之原真人)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把语境也补上啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短一句就把真人形容透彻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.92,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子说啥!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嘛 擦 缺几
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一句深奥的名言诞生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:54.60,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嘛 擦 缺几！ 井之原真人(回顾起其一生)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人生中到底发生什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不会是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你捅了侧腹很痛而已啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我把棒球赛的日程都定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是Little Busters的首次比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余下时日不多 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介你听好 我们还需要以下几样东西才能打比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余队员 练习时间 你以外的队员的干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剩余队员啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙说了两次剩余队员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人这么说肯定有他的想法 别追究了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真没有 对不起了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我摸遍你全身把白痴传给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余队员现在开始找就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打棒球最少需要9人啊 还剩5人 找得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说谦吾你把自己除外了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 招集队员的任务就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招集队员?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长和陌生人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 耳机?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 铃!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招集剩下5人 这就是你的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 将铃派入女生宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把女学生招进Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么选女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是因为男的居多太乏味了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是铃 成功潜入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先向人打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的女生似乎即使到了下午打招呼也说早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太冗长了 是内行人就应该说早好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪方面的内行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 我发现了一个重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速说一遍「Oliver Sauce」 听起来很像「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定好了吗 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oliver Sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务失败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那「俺是齐藤」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来有点像「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 是齐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来超像的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个头!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你自己想一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是齐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫齐藤啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是铃 任务失败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 按常理说晚上好试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 拉她入队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对棒球有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枣同学有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒不了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没兴趣哦 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 枣同学 这是某种新游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对棒球有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…不会不知道本小姐笹濑川佐佐美是垒球社的下任队长候补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你是学园人气第一的枣恭介学长的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且与剑道社的英雄宫泽同学以及一个肌肉白痴很熟络
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用这么跩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你丫是英雄?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这评价算中肯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 告诉她宫泽每次泡澡时都穿着衣服 还把袜子套在脑袋上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢骂我蠢蛋!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个 给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜 很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐佐美大人 太华丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时起 我们被恭介心血来潮卷了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过恭介本人还是一如既往地抱着漫画看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那足以引来其他班级女生围观的阅读姿态 该如何形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说神圣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑 气愤 时而抽泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那一成不变如少年般多彩的表情吸引着旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止都在一起的我们毕业后也可能各奔东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能说的是 一年后恭介肯定不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做只有现在做得到的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我也来试着拉Little Busters的队员吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时起我也如是决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟最先提出想和大家一起做些什么的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先打声招呼再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 世上有很多不可思议的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如甜点和甜点和甜点 所以甜点从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)\bord0\pos(428,370)\blur1}第1话\N队名就叫…Little Busters
