Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树 来打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队名是Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介 还谈这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去招集队员吧 我可全指望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务开始!
